de.oaam.model.oaam.allocations

Interface TaskAssignment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ModeDependentElementA, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA, VariantDependentElementA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TaskAssignmentImpl

    public interface TaskAssignment
extends OaamBaseElementA, VariantDependentElementA, ModeDependentElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Task Assignment'. A allocations of a function to a device.

    The following features are supported:

    • Capability
    • Task
    • Device
    • Schedules
    See Also:
    AllocationsPackage.getTaskAssignment()
